## Remarks

<span data-ttu-id="23ecc-102">运行状况终结点用于执行评估组件的运行状况的运行状况检查。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="23ecc-102">Health endpoints are used to perform health checks that assess the health of a component.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="23ecc-103">运行状况终结点可用于:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="23ecc-103">Health endpoints can be used to:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="23ecc-104">通知业务流程工具终止未通过关键运行状况检查的进程。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="23ecc-104">Notify orchestration tools to kill a process that is failing a critical health check.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="23ecc-105">通过跟踪和提供有关服务可用性和性能的警报, 作为监视工具的早期问题指示器。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="23ecc-105">Serve as an early problem indicator for monitoring tools by tracking and providing alerts about the availability and performance of a service.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="23ecc-106">`ServiceHealthBehavior`是一个 WCF 服务行为, 它扩展 IServiceBehavior 并派生<xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceHealthBehaviorBase>自。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="23ecc-106">`ServiceHealthBehavior` is a WCF service behavior that extends IServiceBehavior and derives from <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceHealthBehaviorBase>.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="23ecc-107">将实例添加<xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceDescription.Behaviors?displayProperty=nameWithType>到集合会启用以下功能: `ServiceHealthBehavior`</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="23ecc-107">Adding a `ServiceHealthBehavior` instance to the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceDescription.Behaviors?displayProperty=nameWithType> collection enables the following:</span></span>

-   <span data-ttu-id="23ecc-108">**服务运行状况发布:** 可以通过`?health`查询字符串使用 HTTP/GET 请求来显示服务特定的详细信息, 如服务状态、限制计数和容量。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="23ecc-108">**Publication of Service Health:** Service-specific details such as service state, throttle counts, and capacity can be displayed using an HTTP/GET request with the `?health` query string.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="23ecc-109">在对错误的 WCF 服务进行故障排除时, 了解并轻松访问显示的信息是极其重要的。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="23ecc-109">Knowing and easily having access to the information displayed is of paramount importance when troubleshooting a misbehaving WCF service.</span></span>

-   <span data-ttu-id="23ecc-110">**返回 HTTP 响应代码:** 可以在查询字符串中指定 HTTP/GET health 探测请求的 HTTP 状态代码。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="23ecc-110">**Return of HTTP response codes:** One can specify in the query string the HTTP status code for an HTTP/GET health probe request.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="23ecc-111">运行状况终结点仅在其运行状况监视的组件上下文中有意义。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="23ecc-111">A health endpoint is only meaningful in the context of the component whose health it monitors.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="23ecc-112">它没有其他意义或用途。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="23ecc-112">It has no other meaning or purpose.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="23ecc-113">因此, 其运行状况是指组件的运行状况的管道。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="23ecc-113">As such, its health is a conduit to the health of the component.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="23ecc-114">客户端*应*假定运行状况终结点返回的 HTTP 响应代码适用于整个组件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="23ecc-114">Clients *should* assume that the HTTP response code returned by the health endpoint is applicable to the entire component.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="23ecc-115">这与使用运行状况检查的当前基础结构工具 (例如负载均衡器、服务发现等) 所期望的行为兼容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="23ecc-115">This is compatible with the behavior expected by current infrastructural tooling that utilize health checks, such as load-balancers, service discoveries, and others.</span></span>

### <a name="enable-a-health-endpoint"></a><span data-ttu-id="23ecc-116">启用运行状况终结点</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="23ecc-116">Enable a health endpoint</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="23ecc-117">可以通过两种方式来指定如何公开运行状况终结点并发布 WCF 服务运行状况信息:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="23ecc-117">There are two ways to specify how to expose the health endpoint and publish WCF service health information:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="23ecc-118">通过使用配置文件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="23ecc-118">By using a configuration file.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="23ecc-119">例如:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="23ecc-119">For example:</span></span>

   ```xml
   <behaviors>
     <serviceBehaviors>
       <behavior name="DefaultBehavior">
         <serviceHealth httpGetEnabled="true"/>
       </behavior>
     </serviceBehaviors>
   </behaviors>
   ```

- <span data-ttu-id="23ecc-120">通过.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="23ecc-120">Programmatically.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="23ecc-121">下面的代码片段使用C#来公开运行状况终结点:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="23ecc-121">The following code fragment uses C# to expose the health endpoint:</span></span>

    ```csharp
    ServiceHost host = new ServiceHost(typeof(Service1),
        new Uri("http://jconde-dev1:81/Service1"));
    ServiceHealthBehavior healthBehavior =
                host.Description.Behaviors.Find<ServiceHealthBehavior>();
    if (healthBehavior == null)
    {
        healthBehavior = new ServiceHealthBehavior();
    }
    //healthBehavior.HttpGetEnabled = false;
    //healthBehavior.HttpsGetEnabled = false;
    host.Description.Behaviors.Add(healthBehavior);
    ```
